            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">100+</div>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Interactive Lessons<br/><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.9;">(Grammar & Vocabulary)</span></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">AI-Powered</div>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Daily Content<br/><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.9;">(Fresh Exercises Daily)</span></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Free</div>
                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">Forever<br/><span style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.9;">(No Hidden Costs)</span></p>
